<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Resource Request: Loan Resources Personnel Needed</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin:
      0; padding: 20px; color: #333; } .email-container { background-color:
      #ffffff; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border-radius:
      8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } .banner {
      background-color: #007bff; color: #ffffff; text-align: center; padding:
      20px; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; } .banner h1 { font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold; margin: 0; } .header { text-align: center; padding:
      20px 0; } .header p { color: #555; font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 10px; }
      .details-box { background-color: #f8f8f8; border-radius: 8px; padding:
      20px; margin: 20px 0; } .details-box ul { list-style: none; padding: 0;
      margin: 0; } .details-box li { font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: #333; } .details-box li strong { font-weight: bold; color: #007bff;
      } .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color:
      #007bff; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 16px; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold;
      } .btn:hover { background-color: #0056b3; } .footer { text-align: center;
      color: #999; font-size: 12px; padding-top: 20px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <div class="email-container">
      <!-- Banner for Subject -->
      <div class="banner">
        <h1>Resource Request: Loan Resources Personnel Needed</h1>
      </div>

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="header">
        <p><strong>Hello,</strong></p>
        <p><strong>I am {{PM_firstName}} {{PM_lastName}},</strong>
          currently overseeing project requirements for the site listed below.
          We require additional personnel resources, and I would appreciate your
          assistance in meeting this need.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Details Box -->
      <div class="details-box">
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Site ID:</strong> {{siteId}}</li>
          <li><strong>Scope:</strong> {{scope}}</li>
          <li><strong>Region:</strong> {{region}}</li>
          <li><strong>Target Cost:</strong> {{targetCost}}</li>
          <li><strong>Remarks:</strong> {{PMRemarks}}</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <p style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">Kindly review the request
        and provide your response at your earliest convenience. Your support is
        crucial for the timely completion of this project.</p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px;">Thank you very much for your attention to this
        matter.</p>
      <a href="[Link to respond or contact]" class="btn">Respond to Request</a>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy;
          {{year}}
          <strong>Omnicom Solutions Limited</strong>. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>